*     word2.spt - Fixed-column record parsing

      PAT      =  POS(0) LEN(4) . WHEN
+                 TAB(6) ARB . WHO " :"
+                 TAB(24) REM . WHAT
LOOP  LINE     =  INPUT                            :F(END)
      LINE     ?  PAT                              :F(LOOP)
      OUTPUT   =  WHO " invented the " WHAT " in " WHEN  :(LOOP)
END
